    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <h3>Is Claude better for writing?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Claude consistently produces more natural prose and handles long-form better than any other AI assistant available today.</p>
    <h3>Which is better for coding?</h3>
    <p>Claude for large refactoring and codebase analysis; ChatGPT for quick scripts, debugging, and data analysis with Code Interpreter.</p>
    <h3>Can I use both together?</h3>
    <p>Absolutely. Many professionals now use Claude for writing and document analysis while relying on ChatGPT for everything else, including image generation, web research, and coding.</p>
    <h3>Does ChatGPT have a better free tier?</h3>
    <p>Yes. ChatGPT's free tier offers GPT-4o with daily usage limits plus limited DALL-E 3 access. Claude's free tier is more restricted with lower rate limits.</p>
